            <h1>Diversified Asset Classes Exposure</h1>
            <p>Jeremy Grantham's GMO Benchmark-Free Allocation III (GBMFX), Steven Leuthold's Core Fund (LCORX), Ivy Asset Management's Asset Strategy (WASAX) and PIMCO All Asset (PASDX) managed by Rob Arnott in Research Affiliated are all excellent funds which have flexible exposures over diversified asset classes including US Equity, Foreign Equity, Real Estate Investment Trust (REIT), Commodities, US bonds and Foreign bonds.</p>
             <ul>
